# ================================================================
# HIREFLOW ETL AUTOMATION FRAMEWORK — .gitignore
# ================================================================

# ── CREDENTIALS & SECRETS (NEVER commit these) ──────────────────
config/.env
*.env
.envrc

# ── PROJECT GENERATED FILES ──────────────────────────────────────
# Logs generated every run
logs/
*.log

# HTML reports generated by pytest / report_generator
reports/
htmlcov/

# DuckDB local database file (training data)
data/hireflow.duckdb
data/hireflow.duckdb.wal
*.duckdb
*.duckdb.wal

# Source CSV files (generated by generate_data.py, not source code)
data/source/
data/expected/

# ── DBT GENERATED FILES ───────────────────────────────────────────
dbt_hireflow/target/
dbt_hireflow/logs/
dbt_hireflow/dbt_packages/
.dbt/

# ── PYTHON STANDARD ───────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
*.egg
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
dist/
build/
.installed.cfg
MANIFEST

# ── VIRTUAL ENVIRONMENTS ─────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.venv
env/
venv/
ENV/
env.bak/
venv.bak/
__pypackages__/

# ── PYTEST & TESTING ─────────────────────────────────────────────
.pytest_cache/
.tox/
.nox/
.coverage
.coverage.*
coverage.xml
*.cover
nosetests.xml
.hypothesis/

# ── JUPYTER NOTEBOOKS ────────────────────────────────────────────
.ipynb_checkpoints
profile_default/
ipython_config.py

# ── PACKAGING & DISTRIBUTION ─────────────────────────────────────
pip-log.txt
pip-delete-this-directory.txt
wheels/
share/python-wheels/
develop-eggs/
downloads/
sdist/
var/
parts/

# ── TYPE CHECKERS & LINTERS ──────────────────────────────────────
.mypy_cache/
.dmypy.json
dmypy.json
.pyre/
.pytype/
.ruff_cache/
cython_debug/

# ── PYENV / PIPENV / POETRY / PDM ────────────────────────────────
.pdm-python
.pdm-build/
.pixi
.pypirc

# ── DOCUMENTATION BUILD ──────────────────────────────────────────
docs/_build/
/site

# ── PYBUILDER / PYINSTALLER ──────────────────────────────────────
.pybuilder/
target/
*.manifest
*.spec

# ── SCRAPY ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.scrapy

# ── CELERY ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
celerybeat-schedule
celerybeat.pid

# ── SAGEMATH ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.sage.py

# ── SPYDER / ROPE ────────────────────────────────────────────────
.spyderproject
.spyproject
.ropeproject

# ── CURSOR / ABSTRA ──────────────────────────────────────────────
.cursorignore
.cursorindexingignore
.abstra/

# ── MARIMO ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
marimo/_static/
marimo/_lsp/
__marimo__/

# ── OS FILES ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ── IDE FILES ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# VS Code (keep .vscode/extensions.json if you want — optional)
.vscode/settings.json
.vscode/launch.json
# JetBrains
.idea/
*.iml

# ── WHAT WE KEEP IN GIT (our actual source code) ─────────────────
# ✅ config/config.yml         → project rules
# ✅ config/logging_config.py  → logging setup
# ✅ config/config_loader.py   → config reader
# ✅ connectors/               → all connector code
# ✅ validators/               → all validator code
# ✅ tests/                    → all pytest files
# ✅ dbt_hireflow/models/      → dbt SQL models
# ✅ dbt_hireflow/tests/       → dbt test definitions
# ✅ scripts/generate_data.py  → data generator
# ✅ scripts/report_generator.py
# ✅ .devcontainer/            → Codespaces setup
# ✅ .github/workflows/        → GitHub Actions
# ✅ requirements.txt
# ✅ README.md
```
```
SAVE: Cmd+S
```

---

## 📌 KEY ADDITIONS EXPLAINED
```
WHAT WAS MISSING          WHY WE ADDED IT
──────────────────────    ──────────────────────────────────
config/.env               Your DB passwords — NEVER commit
logs/                     Auto-generated log files per run
reports/                  Auto-generated HTML reports
data/source/              CSV files we generate, not source code
data/hireflow.duckdb      Local DB file — generated, not code
dbt_hireflow/target/      dbt compiled SQL — auto-generated
.dbt/                     dbt profile with credentials
.DS_Store                 Mac system files — irrelevant to code
.vscode/settings.json     Your personal IDE settings